{"pageProps":{"id":["lang/go/basic/pkg-import.adoc"],"postInfo":{"type":"adoc","doc":{"title":"Go: package 和 import","author":"weily","tags":[],"version":"1.0","date":1590336000000,"content":"<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>类似于 Java，Go 语言的代码是以 package 的方式组织起来的。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>文件的第一行是包声明。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> mypkg</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>在一个包中，以大写字符开头的名称会被暴露出来。比如 <code>math</code> 包中的 <code>Pi</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>在导入一个包时，可以导入整个包，比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> main\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> ( <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"fmt\"</span>; <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"math\"</span> )\n\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">main</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span></span> {\n\tfmt.Println(math.Pi)\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>也可以只导入包的一部分，比如下例中的 <code>rand</code> 是从 <code>math</code> 包中指明导入的：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">package</span> main\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> ( <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"fmt\"</span>; <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"math/rand\"</span> )\n\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">main</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span></span> {\n\tfmt.Println(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"New random integer:\"</span>, rand.Intn(<span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>))\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>"},"toc":{"type":"simple","title":"Go 语言基础","description":"这里是 Go 语言 XXXXXX","toc":[{"title":"基础","path":"basic.adoc"},{"title":"函数","path":"func.adoc"},{"title":"变量","path":"var.adoc"},{"title":"基本类型","path":"basic-types.adoc"},{"title":"字符串","path":"string.adoc"},{"title":"指针","path":"ptr.adoc"},{"title":"数组和切片","path":"array-slice.adoc"},{"title":"映射","path":"map.adoc"},{"title":"结构：struct","path":"struct.adoc"},{"title":"接口：interface","path":"itf.adoc"},{"title":"type 关键字","path":"type.adoc"},{"title":"for 语句","path":"for.adoc"},{"title":"if 语句","path":"if.adoc"},{"title":"switch 语句","path":"switch.adoc"},{"title":"defer 语句","path":"defer.adoc"},{"title":"并发","path":"concurrency.adoc"},{"title":"包和导入","path":"pkg-import.adoc"}]}}},"__N_SSG":true}